data.description: Surrounded by the Majestic Nature of Arkansas, this beauty is just that. MAJESTIC.Large game room, 3 good sized bedrooms, an office off the kitchen or bonus room. Living room, dining and kitchen give an open ranch type feeling. The views & land spectacular. Almost 20 acres, 15 acres of pasture land is cross-fenced (688,941 sqft) 4 wheeler trails, Over 3  (127,196 sqft)acres of Timber and 1 acre (43,560sqft) where home sits. This peaceful property has a pond, Grain Silo & well pump. Large Shop is 5040 sqft insulated w/heat, air, water and fully wired with 1/2 bath a& Overhead compressor system with automatic roll-up door. Property has separate Electrical meter for shop. There is a small metal shed behind the house.  This magnificent slice of Heaven can be yours if you call right away.  SQ approximate, measuring encouraged.  SEE AGENT REMARKS & ONLINE DOCS FOR MORE INFORMATION
